---
title: Chermoula Beef Bowl with Veggie Couscous & Lemon Yoghurt
description: Get a load of this meal that's brimming with colour and flavour. With a fluffy (and sneaky) veggie couscous as the base for mildly spiced beef mince and a refreshing cucumber salad, all the elements come together for a delightful explosion of taste!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chermoula-beef-bowl-0a610de9.jpg
